Package: Nori
Title: Wrappers and add-ons for BentoBox functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Eric", "Davis", email = "esdavis@live.unc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: BentoBox gives users the ability to create and precisely control genomic plots in R. Nori extends BentoBox with useful wrappers and additional functionality.
